high_descs: turn around, take two steps, turn right, walk past counter, turn right, walk to counter, turn right
open cabinet below, take plate out, close cabinet
turn around, walk forward, turn right to face stove
put plate in microwave, turn it on, take plate out when it turns off
move two steps to the left
Turn around, take a right, walk around the counter to the right and turn right to face the counter.
Open the lower left cabinet, pick up the black plate inside and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the white stove on the right.
Put the black plate in the microwave above the stove, heat it, remove it and close the door.
Turn left and face the small counter on the right next to the stove.
Put the heated plate on the small counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated plate on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around to go forward toward the table, then turn right and go around the counter, go toward the coffee maker, then turn right to face the counter.
Open the leftmost cabinet beneath the counter, take out the plate, then close it.
Turn around and go forward, then turn right at the stove and look up to the microwave.
Put the plate in the microwave, heat it up, then take it out.
Go to the counter to your left.
Put the plate on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm plate on the counter.
